attributeSource.infoString2: Coldwell Banker Residential Brokerage - Palm Springs

data.description: Beautifully updated 4 bedroom, 2 bath pool home located in Quail Point.  Highly upgraded HUE Smart-Home. Pool, lighting, alarm and climate controlled all from an app on your phone. Owned solar keeps your electric bills low.  The open concept floor plan is perfect for intimate or large gatherings.  High end furnishings can be included.  This is a great home for full or part time residence.  This home has been a very popular vacation rental.  Awesome pebble-tech pool and spa area with gas fire pit, customizable LED lighting and stunning views of the mountains.  No land lease (you own the land) and no HOA.  A two car garage with direct access.  Brand new Pentair pool heater.  Newer top of the line A/C with Air Scrubber.  Too many other upgrades to list.  This is the one you have been searching for!
